Red5 Server Kit
=====================================
This kit includes AS2 compiler and component classes, as well as Tomcat libraries necessary to launch Red5 Media Server 1.0.RC1 
Compiler included is for OSX, but the compiler website has binaries for Windows and Linux platforms as well.

Package includes:
* Tomcat plugins for Red5 server 
* MTASC 1.12 for OSX
  http://www.mtasc.org/
* Macromedia Flash MX 2004 libraries

Examples (OSX)
=====================================
> export PATH=bin:mx2004/First Run/Classes:$PATH
> ./mtasc -cp "." -swf yourApplication.swf -mx com/example/Main.as -v